des:
Ask for facts about Kalamazoo RESA , and learn about how K-RESA is improving education in Kalamazoo County

To start, just say "Alexa, launch About Kalamazoo RESA" or "Alexa, open About Kalamazoo RESA" to learn something new.

At anytime, you can stop by saying "Alexa, stop"
